room_title: Escape room "The Doll House" by A Room with a Clue in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: Step into a nightmarish and sinister lair of a criminal. Hiding here in a secret room of a condemned house, he has gathered all of his... friends... to keep him company. Explore the Doll House, try to unravel the horrifying story of the killer's past, and escape!
